# Netlify / Cloudflare Pages SPA fallback.
# Any path without an extension (i.e. app routes like /cycle, /tasks/inbox,
# /review/cycle/2026-04-13) serves the built index.html with a 200 status
# so the client-side router picks up the route. Files (assets, wasm, svg)
# take precedence — the rule only fires if no static file matched.
/*    /index.html   200
